show.description: One wedding… Two breakups… The boss's life takes an unexpected turn with the entry of a third girl!" Sonia – a middle-class designer, is fighting for her grandmother's life while paying off a debt of three lakhs. At the same time, the entry of a new boss, Queen, becomes a hot topic in the office. The story of a couple who got married but did not live together is confusing between scenes. That boss is no one… her husband! Obstacles, wrongdoers, betrayals in love, company stakes, design competitions – how did a smart girl face it all? Did the truth come out in the design theft case? Did Sonia win? Did she find love?
